<br>
For example (and simplifying the numbers just for the sake of it) if I get hit for 500 damage, 400 after AF calculations and 265 after chain absorb (400-500x27%), will each lvl of AP reduce 10% out of 500, 400 or 265? (i.e. 265 -50, 265 -40 or 265 -26.5)<br>
<br>
